<br>
Conquest is a guild of powergamers, and as such they might have slightly different beliefs about how the game should be played than others, but it seems to me that they have gone out of their way to be helpful, especially since they reformed as conquest.<br>
<br>
They dont HAVE to come help save fear breaks, but they ( and of course many others like IF, 7D etc) do.  <br>
<br>
Contrary to popular belief, they DONT eat babies etc.  Though some of them are extremely opinionated, that doesnt make them evil.<br>
<br>
Some of the previous flames about SA were substatiated, and many were not.  They are not saints (who is..), but they certainly arent devils either.<br>
